query:
SELECT 
  MIN(orderDate) as primeira_data,
  MAX(orderDate) as ultima_data,
  COUNT(*) as total_pedidos,
  DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate), MIN(orderDate)) as dias_cobertos
FROM orders
